### 3. **Kalkulator Tipów (Java)**

**Opis**: Prosty program w Javie do obliczania napiwków w restauracji.

**Kod**: `TipCalculator.java`
```java
import java.util.Scanner;

public class TipCalculator {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner scanner = new Scanner(System.in);
        System.out.println("Restaurant Tip Calculator");
        
        try {
            System.out.print("Enter bill amount ($): ");
            double bill = scanner.nextDouble();
            System.out.print("Enter tip percentage (e.g., 15 for 15%): ");
            double tipPercentage = scanner.nextDouble();
            
            if (bill < 0 || tipPercentage < 0) {
                throw new IllegalArgumentException("Bill and tip percentage must be non-negative.");
            }
            
            double tip = bill * (tipPercentage / 100);
            double total = bill + tip;
            
            System.out.printf("\nBill: $%.2f\n", bill);
            System.out.printf("Tip: $%.2f\n", tip);
            System.out.printf("Total: $%.2f\n", total);
        } catch (Exception e) {
            System.out.println("Error: " + e.getMessage());
        } finally {
            scanner.close();
        }
    }
}
